{"tid":2497864,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"話反esl=奴隸同鍾意uefa果d點算好？","createTime":"2021-04-20T20:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T20:52:12.000Z","uid":60432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ca96980a8e4e0c021a106ed6b0e55d5286bde886","tid":2497864,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T20:37:44.000Z","msg":"歐超聯得以推動，摩根大通在背後做金主為其中一主因，當中參賽球隊更可獲過億的「獎金」看似非常着數。不過，有傳摩根大通今次的出資其實是一次債務融資協議，協議更長達23年，消息更指15支參賽球隊需要簽訂償還協議，平均每年要還2.64億歐元，所謂的「迎新獎金」其實亦非獎金，只是球會預支的獎金收入，假如球隊中途退賽，亦需作出償還。不過，對於上述的報道，摩根大通就不作評價。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌uefa係屎係吸血鬼，打多左場仲少錢左。<br />\n原來搞esl借人錢打工咁on9,就係對球會最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46be3fee15a5323166de8a10edf1dc96b2b5c0a","tid":2497864,"uid":209773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T20:43:26.000Z","msg":"每年要還2.64億歐元？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n球會攞得佢3.幾億，點樣每年要還2.6億"},{"pid":"56776a542226034ee8547219a5de7f2800049d0a","tid":2497864,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f46be3fee15a5323166de8a10edf1dc96b2b5c0a","tid":2497864,"uid":209773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T20:43:26.000Z","msg":"每年要還2.64億歐元？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n球會攞得佢3.幾億，點樣每年要還2.6億"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T20:44:23.000Z","msg":"息？"},{"pid":"656c8efcac493045d29630a596959b40cda666ca","tid":2497864,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f46be3fee15a5323166de8a10edf1dc96b2b5c0a","tid":2497864,"uid":209773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T20:43:26.000Z","msg":"每年要還2.64億歐元？<img src=\"/ass